                    Section 3 - Debugging
1 - Step Through Debugging
  - Dev Tools provides developers with a powerful step through debugger
  - Ctrl+shift+p allows for doing autocomplete which will be similar to clicking on items
  - Ctrl+p will allow for a file search
    - This will search all files on the current webpage
